{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.stripSuffix\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Slice</span>.<span class=\"name\">stripSuffix</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">suff</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.stripSuffix","kind":"def","line":579,"name":"String.Slice.stripSuffix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L579-L581"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.stripSuffix\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">stripSuffix</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">suff</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.stripSuffix","kind":"def","line":575,"name":"String.stripSuffix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L575-L577"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropSuffix\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropSuffix</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ρ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pat</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ρ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Pattern/Basic.html#String.Slice.Pattern.BackwardPattern\">Slice.Pattern.BackwardPattern</a> <span class=\"fn\">pat</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `pat` matches a suffix of `s`, returns the remainder. Returns `s` unmodified\notherwise.\n\nUse `String.dropSuffix?` to return `none` when `pat` does not match a prefix.\n\nThis is a cheap operation because it does not allocate a new string to hold the result.\nTo convert the result into a string, use `String.Slice.copy`.\n\nThis function is generic over all currently supported patterns.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix \" blue\" == \"red green\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix \"bluu \" == \"red green blue\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix 'e' == \"red green blu\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix Char.isLower == \"red green blu\".toSlice`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropSuffix","kind":"def","line":555,"name":"String.dropSuffix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L555-L573"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.stripPrefix\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Slice</span>.<span class=\"name\">stripPrefix</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">pre</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.stripPrefix","kind":"def","line":551,"name":"String.Slice.stripPrefix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L551-L553"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.stripPrefix\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">stripPrefix</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s </span><span class=\"fn\">pre</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.stripPrefix","kind":"def","line":547,"name":"String.stripPrefix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L547-L549"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropPrefix\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropPrefix</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ρ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pat</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ρ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Pattern/Basic.html#String.Slice.Pattern.ForwardPattern\">Slice.Pattern.ForwardPattern</a> <span class=\"fn\">pat</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `pat` matches a prefix of `s`, returns the remainder. Returns `s` unmodified\notherwise.\n\nUse `String.dropPrefix?` to return `none` when `pat` does not match a prefix.\n\nThis is a cheap operation because it does not allocate a new string to hold the result.\nTo convert the result into a string, use `String.Slice.copy`.\n\nThis function is generic over all currently supported patterns.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix \"red \" == \"green blue\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix \"reed \" == \"red green blue\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix 'r' == \"ed green blue\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix Char.isLower == \"ed green blue\".toSlice`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropPrefix","kind":"def","line":527,"name":"String.dropPrefix","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L527-L545"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropSuffix?\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropSuffix?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ρ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pat</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ρ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Pattern/Basic.html#String.Slice.Pattern.BackwardPattern\">Slice.Pattern.BackwardPattern</a> <span class=\"fn\">pat</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `pat` matches a suffix of `s`, returns the remainder. Returns `none` otherwise.\n\nUse `String.dropSuffix` to return the slice\nunchanged when `pat` does not match a suffix.\n\nThis is a cheap operation because it does not allocate a new string to hold the result.\nTo convert the result into a string, use `String.Slice.copy`.\n\nThis function is generic over all currently supported patterns.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix? \" blue\" == some \"red green\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix? \"bluu \" == none`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix? 'e' == some \"red green blu\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropSuffix? Char.isLower == some \"red green blu\".toSlice`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropSuffix?","kind":"def","line":507,"name":"String.dropSuffix?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L507-L525"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropPrefix?\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">dropPrefix?</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">ρ</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a>}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">pat</span> : <span class=\"fn\">ρ</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Pattern/Basic.html#String.Slice.Pattern.ForwardPattern\">Slice.Pattern.ForwardPattern</a> <span class=\"fn\">pat</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `pat` matches a prefix of `s`, returns the remainder. Returns `none` otherwise.\n\nUse `String.dropPrefix` to return the slice\nunchanged when `pat` does not match a prefix.\n\nThis is a cheap operation because it does not allocate a new string to hold the result.\nTo convert the result into a string, use `String.Slice.copy`.\n\nThis function is generic over all currently supported patterns.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix? \"red \" == some \"green blue\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix? \"reed \" == none`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix? 'r' == some \"ed green blue\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"red green blue\".dropPrefix? Char.isLower == some \"ed green blue\".toSlice`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.dropPrefix?","kind":"def","line":487,"name":"String.dropPrefix?","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L487-L505"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.nextUntil\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">nextUntil</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.nextUntil","kind":"def","line":483,"name":"String.nextUntil","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L483-L485"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Pos.Raw.nextUntil\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Pos</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">nextUntil</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Repeatedly increments a position in a string, as if by `String.Pos.Raw.next`, while the predicate\n`p` returns `false` for the character at the position. Stops incrementing at the end of\nthe string or when `p` returns `true` for the current character.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `let s := \"   a  \"; (Pos.Raw.nextUntil s Char.isWhitespace 0).get s = ' '`\n\n* `let s := \"   a  \"; (Pos.Raw.nextUntil s Char.isAlpha 0).get s = 'a'`\n\n* `let s := \"a  \"; (Pos.Raw.nextUntil s Char.isWhitespace 0).get s = ' '`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Pos.Raw.nextUntil","kind":"def","line":470,"name":"String.Pos.Raw.nextUntil","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L470-L481"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Internal.nextWhileImpl\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">nextWhileImpl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Internal.nextWhileImpl","kind":"def","line":466,"name":"String.Internal.nextWhileImpl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L466-L468"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.nextWhile\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">nextWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Pos.Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.nextWhile","kind":"def","line":462,"name":"String.nextWhile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L462-L464"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Pos.Raw.nextWhile\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Pos</span>.<span class=\"name\">Raw</span>.<span class=\"name\">nextWhile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">p</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Char\">Char</a> → <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">i</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Raw</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String.Pos.Raw\">Raw</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Repeatedly increments a position in a string, as if by `String.Pos.Raw.next`, while the\npredicate `p` returns `true` for the character at the position. Stops incrementing at\nthe end of the string or when `p` returns `false` for the current character.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `let s := \"   a  \"; ((0 : Pos.Raw).nextWhile s Char.isWhitespace).get s = 'a'`\n\n* `let s := \"a  \"; ((0 : Pos.Raw).nextWhile s Char.isWhitespace).get s = 'a'`\n\n* `let s := \"ba  \"; (Pos.Raw.nextWhile s Char.isWhitespace 0).get s = 'b'`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Pos.Raw.nextWhile","kind":"def","line":449,"name":"String.Pos.Raw.nextWhile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L449-L460"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Internal.trimImpl\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">trimImpl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Internal.trimImpl","kind":"def","line":445,"name":"String.Internal.trimImpl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L445-L447"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.trim\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Slice</span>.<span class=\"name\">trim</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.trim","kind":"def","line":441,"name":"String.Slice.trim","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L441-L443"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.trim\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">trim</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.trim","kind":"def","line":437,"name":"String.trim","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L437-L439"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.trimAscii\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">trimAscii</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Removes leading and trailing whitespace from a string.\n\n“Whitespace” is defined as characters for which `Char.isWhitespace` returns `true`.\n\nExamples:\n\n* `\"abc\".trimAscii == \"abc\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"   abc\".trimAscii == \"abc\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"abc \\t  \".trimAscii == \"abc\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"  abc   \".trimAscii == \"abc\".toSlice`\n\n* `\"abc\\ndef\\n\".trimAscii == \"abc\\ndef\".toSlice`\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.trimAscii","kind":"def","line":422,"name":"String.trimAscii","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L422-L435"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.trimLeft\"><span class=\"name\">String</span>.<span class=\"name\">Slice</span>.<span class=\"name\">trimLeft</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/String/Defs.html#String.Slice\">Slice</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.html#String.Slice.trimLeft","kind":"def","line":418,"name":"String.Slice.trimLeft","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Init/Data/String/TakeDrop.lean#L418-L420"}},{"header":"<div 